                <div class="jonra" data-uuid="c9bebf8f484741b383d43154f505d8f9">
                    <h2 data-uuid="69034d664b87493fb29bf42b2f99df4e">The Age of the Flapper</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="92ffb6bc4faa40e297f3cf1e96e83637">Flappers, celebrated here on the cover of LIFE magazine in July 1926, challenged many of society’s ideas about womanhood. They established new rules of speech, dress, and behavior.</p>
                </div>
